Author: circlesproject
Title: [ANN][ICO] Circles - The Future of Social Media Content Appreciation for Web 3.0
Body: New article about Circles and its future on EthereumWiki.com out today!  http://www.ethereumwiki.com/ico/ico-launch-circles-hopes-circulating-content-is-web-3-0s-like-and-share/  We have received 3 ETH in total contributions so far! To find out more we have updated our site: https://circlesproject.io  Also, we are now opening up bounties campaigns, so fee free to PM and we can offer some CRC tokens to those who are able to help us with spreading the word!  We'll be keeping very busy over the next week with helping to spread awareness by reaching out to content creators and letting them know about our future plans and development!  A very big thank you to contributors who have already joined in this far so early on in the beginning stages, onwards from here!
